atically aligned filaments,\nwhich cannot be accounted for by the present Toner and Tu type theory of polar\nactive matter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Jan 2013 20:38:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 26 Jan 2013 13:36:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 23 Apr 2013 10:05:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-02"}
