re an interesting\nopen question is what Internet topology models or generators can fully explain\nor at least reproduce the k-dense properties of the Internet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Jan 2013 01:10:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Feb 2013 01:16:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 7 Aug 2013 20:09:29 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 28 Oct 2013 16:48:47 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 13 Aug 2015 18:42:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-14"}
